helped design
a road that would protect both
humans and

51:29.453 --> 51:35.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
animals. Forty-four crossing
structures now
allow wildlife to move safely
though Banff

51:35.459 --> 51:37.461 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
National Park.

51:37.494 --> 51:43.600 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: There's two basic kinds of
